text.tspan: Happy Anniversary!!
Can you believe it ?? for fuky sake??
Its been 8 months since we became Gf/Bf!
Were getting close to a whole year!
Nini I love you so much!
Of course I have to repeat myself all the time..
Youre the best girlfriend anyone could ever ask for.
Weve been through a lot of arguing
but also a lot of happiness and joy.
And they say..
Love is not real if its not hard
Our love is real
even though it sometimes
we have it tough
we never give up.
And again Nini.
( Thats what makes us really special )
Everyday with you feels complete.
a day without you feels wrong and totally empty.
Like something important is missing.
Nini do you know what that means?
You are a part of my life.
Youre living inside my soul,
my head and my heart everyday!
